commit.message:
Makefile.in (stageprofile_build): Kill redundant target.

	* Makefile.in (stageprofile_build): Kill redundant target.
	* i386.c (mdep_reorg): Don't pad jumps for Athlon.

From-SVN: r67586

+
 2003-06-07  Andreas Jaeger  <aj@suse.de>
 
 	* doc/tm.texi (Costs): Remove DONT_REDUCE_ADDR documentation.
